    {
      "title": "suddenly i am eleven (bonus track)",
      "filename": "/2012/05/suddenly-eleven.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "05",
      "published": "2012-05-19T19:01:00.001Z",
      "updated": "2015-05-16T13:38:54.469Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/photo.JPG\" width=\"200\" />\n<br />\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nsaw a circus tent -&nbsp;in town -&nbsp;today -&nbsp;surrounded -&nbsp;by clowns\n<br />\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nthere were -&nbsp;plainclothes -&nbsp;policemen -&nbsp;in every corner</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\ni did good deed -&nbsp;for the shareholders, -&nbsp;i did this, i wrote:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nunder a bridge -&nbsp;with a spray can -&nbsp;<b>from the gods -&nbsp;</b><b>of my fathers -&nbsp;</b><b>in feathers</b></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<b>i learnt sin -&nbsp;</b>i dismissed that -&nbsp;as bullshit -&nbsp;defyingly - with a -&nbsp;smile</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nthis, i miss:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\na missile -&nbsp;exploding -&nbsp;i hear quanta -&nbsp;talking through - the noise  -&nbsp;and saw </div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nthe filth  -&nbsp;in people -&nbsp;like dad did</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nthe light -&nbsp;in people -&nbsp;like dad did</div>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">the prime -&nbsp;colors  -&nbsp;of creation  -&nbsp;like dad did</span><br />\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n(i meant&nbsp;to say something&nbsp;else entirely)</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\ni meant to say:&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nwill i ever -&nbsp;live to his -&nbsp;expectations -&nbsp;big and small?</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nwell -&nbsp;will you evah?</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nwell then -&nbsp;when you hit -&nbsp;\"it\" -&nbsp;let go -&nbsp;and go home</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\ni'm home -&nbsp;at last -&nbsp;or at least -&nbsp;i'll be there -&nbsp;soon</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "quarup",
      "filename": "/2012/05/closing-arguments.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "05",
      "published": "2012-05-10T12:13:00.000Z",
      "updated": "2015-05-16T13:35:56.666Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; font-size: x-small; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"/images/mannequin-factory/484182.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/484182.jpg\" width=\"147\" /></a></div>\na song -&nbsp;to call it ours -&nbsp;you sit -&nbsp;your miserable self -&nbsp;you sit here -&nbsp;wrapped -&nbsp;in a quilt<br />\n<br />\n[ start again ]<br />\n<br />\na song -&nbsp;to call it yours -&nbsp;in beardsville -&nbsp;running amok -&nbsp;with a shaving kit<br />\nyour old place -&nbsp;where you wait -&nbsp;for your god&nbsp;(a beardless god&nbsp;is as good as any)<br />\n<br />\ni wait for you -&nbsp;you sit -&nbsp;in your suit -&nbsp;singing -&nbsp;our song -&nbsp;there -&nbsp;at the traffic lights -&nbsp;waiting -&nbsp;for the phone to ring -&nbsp;blinking in yellow -&nbsp;my phone is on silent -&nbsp;our song -&nbsp;as ringtone -&nbsp;won't play -&nbsp;the phone will vibrate -&nbsp;penetrate -&nbsp;shake -&nbsp;rattle -&nbsp;and blink<br />\n<br />\nyour miserable self -&nbsp;in the mirror -&nbsp;your phone -&nbsp;decides your fate -&nbsp;we are then doomed -&nbsp;by semiconductors -&nbsp;controlling life -<br />\nas we know it -&nbsp;i rebel against faith -&nbsp;or fate -&nbsp;to conduct my life -&nbsp;to the next traffic light<br />\n<br />\nseek Him there -&nbsp;seek Her -&nbsp;refurbished -&nbsp;in silicon -&nbsp;valedictory -&nbsp;so i spin -&nbsp;our song -&nbsp;one last time</div>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "standing at the edge of the sky",
      "filename": "/2012/05/i-worry-my-triplets-contemplate-letting.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "05",
      "published": "2012-05-07T13:01:00.002Z",
      "updated": "2015-04-25T08:04:53.979Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/Untitled.jpg\" height=\"200\" width=\"200\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\ni worry my triplets&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">contemplate&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">letting it all go&nbsp;sometimes</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">sometimes&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">they stay&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">too close to the edge</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\nmy sisters they are&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">forever static&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\"><br /></span>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">oh! nothingness</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">oh! nothingness</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\"><br /></span>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">staring,&nbsp;never running&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">they chopped off their feet<br />\n<br />\ni saw words in a book they became my window<br />\ni shut it tight to keep the cold outside<br /><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">but why then do I see before the window life itself?<br />\nmy window view has been blocked by a wall of bricks<br /><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">but why then do they see before them the edge staring back?<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">their window view &nbsp;has been blocked by a wall of mist</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\"><br />\noh! nothingness</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\"><br /></span>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">here is the thing life is made of little bricks</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">here is the thing life is made of little bricks</span><br />\n<div>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\"><br /></span></div>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">\n<br />my sisters got a new leader yesterday</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">they think she will change everything<br />\n</span>\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">they think everything will change</span></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "sad sad songs for passover",
      "filename": "/2012/05/sad-sad-songs-for-passover.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "05",
      "published": "2012-05-04T12:18:00.002Z",
      "updated": "2017-11-18T13:35:27.722Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n</div>\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">what do you want to grow up for? grown up people are so sad&nbsp;</span><br />\n<a href=\"/images/mannequin-factory/song.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/song.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a><span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">\n[i thought of nadine as a child, forever watching the wrong cartoons] <br /><br />\nget_back, get back \"to_where_you_once_belong\"&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">i can't remember \"where_the_fuck_that_is\"&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">heathfield? cavendish?<br /><br />\nthis life - is so important - it always is.&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">it is always about life and death all the fucking time and we all break like thin glass.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">our lives are like a dump place we once knew&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">we just didn't know they'd dumped bronzes of heroes</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">that won't fit - the new regime<br /><br /><br /><b style=\"color: red;\">easter - arson - weird_thing - passover - pass_over - the big party</b><br /><span style=\"color: red;\"><b>\neaster - slick - weirdest_thing - passover - pass_over - the biggest party</b></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">what do you want to grow up for? grown up people are so sad&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, monospace; font-size: x-small;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">[i thought, does nadine eat chocolate and does she believe in the easter_bunny?]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nthere is always room for another drop, a raindrop, a teardrop&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot; , &quot;courier&quot; , monospace; font-size: x-small;\">the ocean,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, monospace; font-size: x-small;\">the glass of our lives is never full&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, monospace; font-size: x-small;\">only once in a lifetime, your life&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, monospace; font-size: x-small;\">your life has been a lie</span></div>"
    },
    {
