      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/cap.jpg\" width=\"200\" />\n</div>\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">sorrow fed the tree of life - this cloudy monday</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">dreadnoughts - over diversity - small guns - lots of animosity - obesity<br />\n<br />\nimagine - being called sergei - fueled - by cheap vodka<br />\nin disguise - i am - a gypsy - in disguise<br /><br />\nthey told me - to guard it - never - how to make - sense of it - on the 99th stroke - the poor thing - broke<br /><br />\nwe got moved - down - to caves - in beardsville - i will not - protect you - anymore - white socks - tube socks - teletubbies - on sandals - like jesus the one - from the mall of america - queuing for soup <br /><br />\nimagine - jesus - in disguise - i am - a buddhist in - disguise<br />\n<br />\nthey told me - to guard it - never - how to make - sense of it - on the 99th stroke - the poor thing - broke\n</span></div>"
    },
