      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/mantis.jpg\" height=\"200\" width=\"200\" />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">i was not worried - about things - being off tempo - anymore - I knew - how to dance - to them - and it was very easy - if she just - let me guide her - and so she did - and so we danced <b>(the yellow queen and i)</b> -  we had all the time - in the world - and so we danced<br /><br />\nwe were living in a prison - after all - watched daily - through shattered glass - i thought we had - all the time in the world - and we didn't care - and then we danced - <b>(the yellow queen and i)</b> - and we looked like one...<br /><br />\n[ they bombed the gallery where your pictures showed my queen spinning in shades of pale green ] \n</span></div>"
