tial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">in fear she left for the woods made two of them</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">in shadows licking lemon lips</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">o she can't take it anymore,&nbsp;</span>​with no love left</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\"><br /></span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">look at him, loaded</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">is that you who ate all the lights?</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">it's you no doubt disguised as a pierrot</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">a daffodil eye - so unreal</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">she landed on her left eye</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">that or maybe she got mistaken by a punch bag</span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">licking lemon lips</span><br />\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br /></span></div>\n<div style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; color: #605e5e; font-family: din-next-w01-light, din-next-w02-light, din-next-w10-light, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; max-width: 99.9000015258789%; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" height=\"166\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/206818636&amp;color=0066cc&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>"
