    {
      "title": "nelly",
      "filename": "/2012/04/nelly.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "04",
      "published": "2012-04-11T06:24:00.002Z",
      "updated": "2015-04-26T05:25:17.294Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/photo.JPG\" height=\"200\" width=\"199\" /></div>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">love has feet like his mother  - feet so sore of dithering  -  acrylic colors - over colors -  his mind races, in doubt -   yet she doubts - love's reasons - hammers him - in the head \n<br /><br />(first time i flew on a empty plane i slept all night)\n<br /><br />\nfather he rubs envy's feet  - follows bloodlines  - dripping slowly down  - the dead vine  - his mind lands, in debt  - blinking, she aims right - and hits envy in the heart \n<br /><br />\n(first time i flew on a empty plane i slept all night)</span></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "exit strategy",
      "filename": "/2012/04/exit-strategy.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "04",
      "published": "2012-04-04T13:04:00.000Z",
      "updated": "2015-05-16T13:42:11.181Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/Photo1-1.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"200\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; color: #222222;\">baby's not feeling too good -&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">she's tossing and turning -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">sweat on white silk -&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">moving sideways -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">afraid of falling (apart) -&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">uneasy sleep -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">the workers hammering -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">the room next door -&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">she hears two of them -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">no rhythm no pattern - no music&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">just noise</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #222222;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><br /></span></span>\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; color: #222222;\">outside the traffic jams -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">sirens horns screams -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">she runs to the window -&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">moving sideways -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\">afraid of falling (apart) -&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">the crash was loud -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">the phone rings -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">it is my sister in fear -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">dad was &nbsp;- walking the dog -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">he saw everything -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">he saw lady v &nbsp;-</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;of the shopping cart -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">getting hit by a car</span></span></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "ghostkeeper",
      "filename": "/2012/03/ghostkeeper-this-is-how-things-were.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "03",
      "published": "2012-03-28T12:08:00.000Z",
      "updated": "2016-02-28T16:10:54.388Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<div style=\"text-align: -webkit-auto;\">\n<a href=\"/images/mannequin-factory/photo.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"198\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/photo.JPG\" width=\"200\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">this is how things were:</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">everyone had an opinion -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">about the pictures i took -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">under the influence -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">of adrenaline&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">she&nbsp;would never do -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">any of that anymore:</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">falling off the stage -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">at night</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">i had made no plans -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">beyond breathing -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">and sleeping -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">and never waking up -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">from daydreaming -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">again</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">she&nbsp;would never do -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">any of that anymore:&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">upon seeing the snow angel -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">i took no impulse -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">landed on my back -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">lost air and declared -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">\"</span><b style=\"font-family: 'helvetica neue', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">i hereby become superman</b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">\"</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">i was a mess -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">for days after that -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">but the angel &nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">she is still alive</span><b><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><b><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\"><br /></span></b></span>\n<b><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;\"><br /></span></b></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br/>\n<hr/>\n<br/>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" height=\"20\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/249324034&amp;color=ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "21 days",
      "filename": "/2012/03/blog-post.html",
      "year": "2012",
      "month": "03",
      "published": "2012-03-28T12:02:00.001Z",
      "updated": "2015-05-16T13:41:00.057Z",
      "author": "eKsKog",
      "categories": [],
      "content": "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"/images/mannequin-factory/photo.JPG\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" width=\"240\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">\n</span><br />\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\" trbidi=\"on\">\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">they closed the mannequin factory today&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">- they left a few of us behind -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">naked, like ghosts -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">in ruins...</span><br />\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<b><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></b></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<b><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">in 21 days&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">we will start anew</span></b></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: -webkit-auto;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">but right here, right now -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">you make us feel -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">like tired horses....</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: -webkit-auto;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">..you could have&nbsp;</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">stopped it -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">but no -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">you just left us there -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">overexposed</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: -webkit-auto;\">\n<div>\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">processing - isolation -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">processing - hate...</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">she saw it as before, -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">in shades of grey -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">it happened &nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">because you never &nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">listen to me -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">right there, right then...&nbsp;</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: -webkit-auto;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<b><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">in 21 days&nbsp;</span></b><b><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">it will all be over</span></b></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  ]
}